    <item>
      <title>印度停止向俄罗斯供应受制裁油轮巨头的石油</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/india-stops-taking-russian-oil-delivered-on-sovcomflot-tankers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国的制裁，所有印度炼油厂现在都拒绝接收 PJSC Sovcomflot 油轮上运载的俄罗斯原油，这使得自两年前入侵乌克兰以来蓬勃发展的贸易进一步复杂化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/india-stops-taking-russian-oil-delivered-on-sovcomflot-tankers</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 08:53:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>银行无力填补核电 5 万亿美元的缺口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/filling-nuclear-power-s-5-trillion-hole-is-beyond-the-banks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着公众对原子能的支持浪潮日益高涨，核能官员本周抵达布鲁塞尔。银行家在评估他们的雄心壮志的代价时反应不温不火，他们在离开时感到谦卑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/filling-nuclear-power-s-5-trillion-hole-is-beyond-the-banks</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 08:34:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲股市有望实现 2012 年以来最长涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/european-stocks-on-track-for-longest-winning-run-since-2012</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲股市周五基本持平，守住历史高位，并有望连续第九周上涨，这是自 2012 年以来最长的连续上涨，原因是人们对经济的信心不断增强，而且降息即将到来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/european-stocks-on-track-for-longest-winning-run-since-2012</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 08:23:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
